I remember first hearing this incredible story of the Brawn Formula 1 car and team sitting with my bestie and her husband, Simon Hammerson at their kitchen table and thinking how absolutely unbelievable it was. It took a lot to get here, Simon, but now it’s here and we are so proud of you!! 

Brought to you by creator, showrunner and executive producer @hammaglamma and epic story told by Keanu Reeves - “Braun: The Impossible Formula 1 Story” is out today on Hulu and Disney+. Check it out!! 🚗💨
